{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/TitleEN1.png?t=1737449295\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each character has unique skills and attributes that can be strategically combined based on the needs of battle. Whether you choose a powerful melee warrior or a spellcasting mage, you\u2019ll find a role that suits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/1.gif?t=1737449295\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/TitleEN2.png?t=1737449295\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can choose to form a circle to enhance your attack or line up in a row to increase your speed. With simple switching mechanics, you can quickly respond to the ever-changing battle conditions and fully unleash your team\u2019s potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/2.gif?t=1737449295\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/TitleEN3.png?t=1737449295\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different playstyles complement each other, allowing for rich combat strategies. Explore various possibilities, discover hidden combinations, and find the best synergies to showcase your heroes\u2019 extraordinary strength and style in battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251240/extras/3.gif?t=1737449295\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i